{"tid":1588100,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[勇武也公關!]正確利用白板同傳媒鏡頭嘅方式","createTime":"2019-09-22T16:20:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T14:54:22.000Z","uid":308041,"like":86,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"ac2f843cbd883ede009673a2057c680e89dca18a","tid":1588100,"uid":308041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:20:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1587925/page/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1587925/page/2</a><br />\n睇完上面呢個POST後有感而發<br />\n好多睇直播嘅中老年人都唔明白勇武行動背後嘅原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以建議勇武開工前可以利用一下直播嘅鏡頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">寫白板</span></span>嘅話俾市民知咩事<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fF8DZyR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfF8DZyR.png&h=d0d58b0c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n一塊小小嘅白板好平 勇武要棄裝掉左都唔可惜<br />\n<br />\n用嘅<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">方法有兩種</span></span><br />\n<br />\n1.<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">打底</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">做野之前</span>表明行動目的例如:用火魔法前<br />\n寫:<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">驅狗</span></span><br />\n(表明係為阻擾狗衝而掉)<br />\n<br />\n2.<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">補飛</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">做完之後</span>澄清行動原因例如:私了藍屍之後<br />\n寫:<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">藍屍出手 正當自衛</span></span><br />\n(手足有時行動係要分秒必爭 黎唔切做之前寫白板係正常不過但要記得補飛)<br />\n<br />\n寫嘅<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">字句要盡量簡短</span></span><br />\n不僅係爭取時間<br />\n亦可以讓之後嘅民間記者會有更多解釋空間<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">小弟P牌麻煩幫推到勇武見到為止</span>"},{"pid":"38596508641568238f3ed47782f179476ee77ec6","tid":1588100,"uid":143151,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:22:42.000Z","msg":"加英文！！！！！！！"},{"pid":"fc3147467416a8585739b8f2bf45ea4021959814","tid":1588100,"uid":308041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38596508641568238f3ed47782f179476ee77ec6","tid":1588100,"uid":143151,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:22:42.000Z","msg":"加英文！！！！！！！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:23:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ccedc26cb008e7ee2fd73fda94276d94efa0d34","tid":1588100,"uid":288351,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:24:44.000Z","msg":"cctvb會cut鳩晒你d字"},{"pid":"c6535e4f2025dcc5f85f657ff940d18b28ed5787","tid":1588100,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:26:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"7f30a9f795cfccdcbcbb78bcefe5d718bf78842b","tid":1588100,"uid":308041,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"6ccedc26cb008e7ee2fd73fda94276d94efa0d34","tid":1588100,"uid":288351,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:24:44.000Z","msg":"cctvb會cut鳩晒你d字"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:27:39.000Z","msg":"依家先針對番支持我地嘅淺黃先<br />\n佢地會睇RTHK架<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm